Password Cracking & Hash Analysis üîê

In this lesson, we explored how weak passwords can be cracked and why strong passwords matter.md

- Learned about hashing and generated a Hash of a Password.md
- Cracked hashes using Hashcat.md
- Used Hydra for Brute-Forcing.md
- Saw firsthand how easy it is to break common and short passwords.md

This lesson showed me how attackers exploit weak passwords, reinforced why strong, unique passwords and multi-factor authentication (MFA) are essential for security.md 
This is a great reminder to us never reuse passwords!.md
